\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did she ever buy clothes for you and your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Where were they bought, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No they were - they were - for my sister they were mostly bought at - a small shop on the end of Parson Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 A clothing shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Well it was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 children\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  outfitters you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And where were your clothes bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
My clothes usually came from shops in the town. Just - just for going to school? Up to 1918. Well my father got his - his clothes made a bespok
e tailor and from the age of fifteen he'd take - he used to take me to the same place to get my clothes made there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So you had suits made by a bespoke tailor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What about shoes, did you ever have secondhand shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No. No, always new.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Where did you get those from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Mostly in the town. Yes. They were always proper shoes but at school we wore clogs. Y-s.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Your sisters as well?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Sisters as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did your father ever help your mother with any of the jobs in the house such as cleaning, cooking, washing-up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I think it's very doubtful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did he light the fires in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did he do any decorating or repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh certainly not, he wouldn't do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 He didn't do any repairs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Or improvements?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
No. I'll tell you why either. Well he was the Secretary of the A.E.U., which was a craft union and he believed that every man should do his own job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 He felt as if he was doing somebody else out of a job if he did his own decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes, he would - certainly would not do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It was his own house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It was his own house, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 But he just didn't believe in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did he ever help with dressing or undressing or bathing you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
Oh - he'd help in such ways as - dressing you if - if it was weekend, but during the week of course he was off to work by six o'clock in the morning. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 But he helped at the weekend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did he ever read to you or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes, he - he'd do that when we were tiny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did he ever take you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Certainly. Walks yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did he ever look after you when she was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you have any tasks you had to carry out regularly at home to help your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I hadn't. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Sisters'd help to wash up and that's the limit of what they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How long did they continue to do these takes - after they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 left}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Up to the time that they got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1667174 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 . Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you or your eldest sister ever help the little one with things that she found difficult?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you ever look after her in any other way at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Do you mean look after my sisters? Only by taking - going i
n the park playing, Victoria Park and - taking care they didn't get into trouble.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You sometimes did that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did the younger children ever help you in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Not that I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. We were all in bed by eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Every night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did your mother or anyone else put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 At what age did you put yourself to bed?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh - that takes a bit of doing. I should say - six or seven I should go to bed on my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you share the bedroom or bed with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You had your own bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. In the attic.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What were the sleeping arrangements of the whole family, where did they all sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They - mother and father slept in the front bedroom, my two sisters slept in the back bedroom and I slept in the attic.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 In - in the - in one bedroom there was a - this sounds rather peculiar because
 - there isn't many could - would be able to say this at that time. There was a bathroom cut off the - one of the bedrooms and there was a bath installed in 1899. With hot and cold water. So I never known a place without a bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So you could always have a bath in this little room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 That's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How often did you have a bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh we - as children do you mean? Oh two or three times a week. Yes, because the bath was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When did you have clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Fridays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Every Friday night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. That - that's underclothes of course you're speaking of I - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh well the - the - my sister's have clean frocks on each day. Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 But you had clean underwear once a week?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 In the house, which is the only room apart from the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 In the sort of living room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were there any occasions when they ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When we what? No. Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You always had it in the room other than the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What was her cooking equipment, was it a range or a gas stove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It was a range.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What did you refer to the meals during the days as, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 breakfast}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Dinner and tea. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When was breakfast eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 About eight thirty in the morning because we went to school for nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What members of the family were present for breakfast at that time?
