\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 He was the secretary for the Keighley area.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 There'd be quite a lot of members?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 There
'd be quite a lot of members in that but not as many as there is today of course Because as I've said before, that was a craft union, you could not be a member unless you'd served five years and three months apprenticeship. But now of course that doesn't 
apply. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So he'd be kept very busy in the evenings and he'd have to attend union meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. He went to all union meetings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did he have to do minutes for the meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, there'd be a minute clerk for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 He just kept the books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Books, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 Very}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Do you remember her ever going out and if so with whom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I can't remember her going out. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Finished at five thirty. And he - walk home probably quarter to six to six o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Every one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What about the union meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Apart from the - went to union meetings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How often would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Once a fortnight.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So nine evenings out of ten he'd be at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 He'd be at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And he'd be working on his books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did your father attend any clubs or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did your father take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Never attended the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Never had a bet or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs, such as a boot, sick, funeral, anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 
Co-operative - savings clubs - I think the Co-operative society ran some system whereby you could buy stamps which allowed you to have extra spending for special occasions such as Christmas and so on. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And I think mother'd be in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It was a sort of Christmas club thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 But they never contributed to a sick club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh yes, they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 were in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  sick clubs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did they operate, if you were sick they paid you so much a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They paid you so much a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 In return for which you paid so much a week when you were at work?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did they ever contribute to a funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. They were in a funeral club called the Little Brief which is now become defunct and taken over by the - Victoria Assurance Company.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They paid so much a week to this little Brief?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
What they did in that, it was based at Ingrow Wesley Place Sunday school and what they did for each person that died in - during the year they paid so much. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 
Say there was twelve died during the year whatever they levied on them, whether it was sixpence it was a fund of pay six bob, if it was a shilling they paid twelve bob for a year or if it was a penny, which it was a many a time, pay one shilling.}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They paid this money out to those people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, you paid that as your subscription. You paid on the number of people that died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Depending on the number of people who died that were in the club you were levied accordingly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So it varied from year to year how much you paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Yes. That's right. Yes. But of course it got into a position where it - what it paid out was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 negligible}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  so of course it wrapped up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Do you remember how well you got on with your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh I should think - ordinarily.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You had your differences?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Like any - any other children in a household. But nothing serious.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Was there one of your sisters that you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 As a child who did you play with, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 sisters}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Neighbours generally.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You didn't play too much with your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Where did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 In the street. Or in the park.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you have a yard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. A small one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you ever play in the yard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you have a garden at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So it was either the yard or the street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Or the park.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you ever play at other children's homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Was there anywhere }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 else}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  that you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What games did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Kick-can.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What's kick-can?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
Well you put a can in the middle of the street and kick it and everybody scatters and - gets - get out of sight and the person who's kicked the can has to find - some person who's hiding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Some sort of hide and seek sort of game?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
Yes. We played cricket and balls - ball games in the street. Until the neighbours moved you for fear of their windows. Then you went in the park again.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They didn't mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were you free to play with anyone you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did your parents discourage you from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you have any hobbies when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 At school? Moths - natural history. Breeding caterpillars. Breeding frogs. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you do anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, that was mostly what occupied my time with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you have any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 We always had dogs and cats.
