\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Not that I am aware of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What about your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, not that I am aware of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Not in the union perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were friends ever invited into your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How often would this happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I should say - in winter probably monthly. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When they came would they be offered anything to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 There was plenty to eat. There wouldn't be anything to drink. Yes, there may have been some home made wine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Nothing stronger than that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were there any particular days or occasions when they would invite people round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Weekends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It wouldn't be for a birthday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, just weekends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 Would}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
 you say that the friends invited in were your mother's friends or your father's or were the both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I should say both.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did friends call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Many times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When - would that be frequent or infrequent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Pretty frequent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did neighbours pop in fairly frequently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Without invitations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Without any invitation at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They could be the same could they, neighbours and friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Would they be the same people probably?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did your parents ever go out to visit friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 People often tell us that in those days they made their ow
n amusements, what do you think your parents did when they got together with their friends or neighbours? Did they play music or games or did they just talk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It was mostly talking. If they had a piano they'd - probably get round the piano and somebody'd sing and - and play and that's about all.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did they do this at your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Many people divide society into different social classes or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 groups.}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  In that time before 1918 - did you think of some people belonging to one and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Before 1918? Definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You thought of some people as being in your own class and some in another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Could you tell me what you thought the different classes were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What we should call rich, what we called rich in 
those days which were the manufacturing class, because there's no aristocracy in Keighley so - I never thought of those. And then I thought of the - people who owned the large shops. Next the - working class. The craftsmen working class. And then of cours
e - the slum areas such as Eastwood Square which was very close to the school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were the people there very poor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They were the - very poor people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were the people who lived there mainly unemployed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They were mainly labouring classes. Not all of them but some - a lot of them were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So you divided them mainly into people who employed people and owned engineering shops or mills?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And then the people who owned small businesses such as shops in Keighley and then the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And then an even }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 lower }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 class of people who were quite poor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Which class or group would you say you belonged to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Well - I obviously belonged to the one that was the - craft, didn't I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 In K
eighley at that time I suppose there were quite a lot of skilled men about so there'd be a lot of working class people who'd be reasonably well off?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. I wouldn't say they were well off but - they could manage along.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They had a regular job and were skilled?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Quite a lot of skilled engineers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
What would you say the sort of people were who belonged to the same group as yourself, you said they were mainly skilled, would you say they lived a fairly good life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
I should say they - they had a decent existence. But as regards - what we think' - common place today like putting money in building societies and such things as that, it just didn't happen because there wasn't the - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 money}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  to put in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They didn't have anything to spare?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No. They're living week to week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 In the same group as yourself in the same area, the same way as you lived, would there be say woollen mill operatives or people like that?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. There would. They were skilled men of course a lot of them, wool sorters and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And white collar workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Would you classify them in the same way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Same way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And shop assistants?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What sort of people belonged to the other cla
sses or groups, what about teachers and things like that, would you say they belonged to a better off, higher class sort of group of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Well they were certainly - a cut above. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 
Whether - they were better off financially or not I wouldn't like to say because they were trying to uphold a certain position weren't they in life. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
Whereas - people - like our family could - could dress their children reasonably well and as I say, go to school }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 in clogs}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
. The schoolteacher who had children obviously had to try and keep just a little bit higher. and as I've to older and realize that the schoolteachers salaries was very little above what the craftsman were they were probably actually worse off.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They had difficulty in maintaining this standard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
Can you think any other people who belonged to any other classes other than yourself, what sort of people they were who were in a higher class than yourself or in a lower class than yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Only the - the people - as I've stated, who owned shops an so on which - we thought as children, were better off than us. It }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 doesn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
 necessarily follow they were but we thought so and of course the class of - manufacturers and owners of engineering works of course we never saw them. They lived in large houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 On the outskirts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 That's right. Like Scotland Road and places like that. We never saw them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So they didn't live near you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Your parents didn't discriminate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were you ever told to touch your cap or show respect in some way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I can't remember being told to actually touch my cap but I would - certainly would not have been allowed to
 sit down in a bus or in a train or anything like that while some folk were standing. I'd have to stand up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And that's the way you showed respect for older people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 But not for people of a particular class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, nothing to do with that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So you were never taught to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 touch}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  your cap or do anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Was there anyone you called sir or master or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Only teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in these ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 In the district who were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 considered}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I should say the doctor. Because he lived there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 He actually lived within the district where you lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I suppose the people who were really considered important lived out of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 
that district?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So there would only be the doctor who lived within the district?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Who the people really looked up to sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you come into }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 contact}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  with him at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Many times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When he visited you when you were ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Other than that did you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Why would you say he was considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Well just as the same thing applies today, they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265633\charrsid2571347 still think}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  doctors are important.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Can you give a reason why you think people did think of him as being important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 The only }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 thing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  is that I can think about is of course that in - he's the man you fly to in a crisis isn't he. That's the only reason I can think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It was nothing to do with the class structure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh no. No. No. In fact he used to ride a bicycle in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So they thought he was important simply because he was a help to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 He was a help, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 yes,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  he was the one you flew to.
