\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What did you do at evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Mathematics. Engineering. Engineering drawing. And English.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 These were subjects concerned with your work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 Do}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
 you have any regrets about your education, was there anything you would have liked to have been different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Well If I - if I was living today I definitely carry on longer. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Do you think you benefited generally from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Certainly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 While you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 at}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  school did you have a part time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You never went half time to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So that was really part time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I thought you meant such as newspaper rounds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you go on with that, did you work mornings or afternoons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Alternate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What job was it that you got half time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Working in a textile mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Was this because you couldn't start an apprenticeship until you were a certain age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Fifteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How old were you when you started this job, twelve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Twelve. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And you worked mornings one week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And afternoons another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you get it, the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I simply went to the mill and applied for a job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You went by yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Your parents didn't get it for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Just went. You usually got it by somebody else - in the street who was working at the same pla
ce and said, well, come to work at our place and so you went and got a job and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You just walked up and asked the people for a job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 That's right. You got a job of course in those days straight away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 What exactly did you have to do in this job in the woollen mill.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Taking - full bobbins off the spinning frame and putting empty bobbins on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Is that what they call doffing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. That's the easiest way of putting it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Do you remember what hours you worked during the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Six 'til twelve on the mornings. And - half one to half past five in the afternoons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And you were at school during the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You didn't work on Sunday at all did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What about Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You worked on Saturday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Every week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Just the half day Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you have any holidays with pay while you were half time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What were you paid per week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Five shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Five shillings a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Just the half time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you feel that that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I should imagine - I thought it was pretty poor at that time.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Whether you worked morning or afternoon it was just five shillings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Just the same, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 All of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What was it spent on, do you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 know}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It'd got in general housekeeping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
get on with the other people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Not bad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh fairly decently. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Conditions were quite good in the mill then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Well they weren't bad in the mill I worked in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you feel about the employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It was very seldom we saw him you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So you didn't have any particular feelings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, he'd come }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 through}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  the mill happen once a week and that's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you feel about the work, did you like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I'd say that I was particularly fond of it. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did the job alter your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you do any other part time jobs before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What was your first full time job?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Do you mean when I started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When you left school altogether, did you go into the job that you'd been doing previously half time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
No. I - I went to work for the - now let me get this right first - I went to work for the Corporation Museum in Victoria Park. Training as a museum curator.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How old were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And that was just as you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 How long did you do this job of learning to be a curator?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 I was just going to try and explain to you, you see war broke out in August 1914. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And all my friends went into - of my own a
ge group - went into engineering which was then a munitions work. So - I badgered my parents to let me leave the museum which they eventually did when I was about fifteen years and nine months old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 worked}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  there about a year and nine months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you get this job at the museum?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Because there was - it was - advertised in the press. I applied for it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were there a lot applying for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Quite a lot, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What exactly did you have to do at the museum?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
It was a general - what shall we call it - well what I had to do of course was to - learn the - taxidermy for one thing. And - setting up of cases. That's mostly it - of the time I was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You didn't have to do any cleaning or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh no, no cleaning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Seeing to visitors or anything like this?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Do you remember what you were paid when you were working there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Once you started working full time at the museum did you still give all of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And it still went into the general budget?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Was there just you and the curator at the museum?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Five. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you get on very well with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Who was your employer this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 City Corporation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Who was sort of immediately over you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Curator.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you get on with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You quite liked him did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you feel about this work, did you like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I liked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What did you do after this job?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Engineering. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What made you change from the museum because you'd liked being there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Out - outbreak of war. Well the fact that everybody else was either a soldier or doing something in the mu
nitions and all my friends were - in my age group - were on munitions.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you feel a bit out of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I felt a bit out of it. So I badgered my parents to let me leave which eventually they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Where did you go to work then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 George Wilkinson and Sons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They were general engineers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 General eng - machine tool makers. Bradford Road, Keighley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you get this job, did you just go to the shop and apply?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You just applied by yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Just applied.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You didn't get it through anyone or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What did you do at this job, you became an apprentice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 Came as an apprentice, yes.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You were fifteen at the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What hours did you work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Six o'clock in the morning while five thirty at night.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What hours }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 did you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  do at the museum?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Nine o'clock 'til - twelve o'clock and one o'clock 'til five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Was it a six day week at the museum?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Six day. But not all day Saturday. You finished at dinner on Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And what were your hours at the engineering shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Six o'clock in the morning 'til five thirty at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Quote a lot longer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh yes. That's - that's without the overtime, we had to work over as well because there was a war on. All the - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 law}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  appertaining to juveniles working hours was wiped out of course. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So you'd be working perhaps Sundays would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No. Didn't work any Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What about Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Worked 'til dinner time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 But if you were on overtime would you work in the afternoon as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 We had to work in the afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you have any half days or just the Saturday afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 We had Saturday afternoon off and Sunday off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you get any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What were you paid there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You started at five shillings a week. As an apprentice and you went up a shilling per year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you feel that this was a fair wage or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, I thought it was very poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So that wasn't a bad wage because when you were at the woolen mill you'd have been getting five shillings a week half time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 That's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you give any of the money to your mother then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Gave it all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And that went in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 general}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  household budget?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How did you get on with the other people at the engineering shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How about your employer in the engineering?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes, same applies to him as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How long did you work at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 Wilkinson\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Until - I joined the Army. In 1918.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You stayed at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 Wilkinson\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 From 1915 until 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When you were called up with no break?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You joined the Army at what stage in 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 June. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How long were you in the Army?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Until - the end of 1919.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What jobs have you done since then, since 1919, right until you retired?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Right until I retired? Having - having left the Army I - went to - engineering with Jonathon Gill, Keighley. At the clos
ing of that firm I went to be - a motor engineer for Keighley Corporation buses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How long }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 were you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  at Jonathon Gill's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Two year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And then you went to Keighley Corporation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Buses. Transport. I was a fitter. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 A sort}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  of motor mechanic?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How long did you work for Keighley Corporation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Until - 1932. I worked on them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 That would be for about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Ten years. Ten year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Where did you go then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I went then back to the museum.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You finished in engineering?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I packed up with engineering and went back to - to the museum.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 To the Victoria Park Museum?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 What did you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 The same job as I went for in the first place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 As assistant curator?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 Yes}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 How long did you stay at that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Until 1965. Cliff Castle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did the museum close at Victoria Park?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It was transferred. Castle. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you become curator?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I was - chief assistant when I retired.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When you started there you were second or third official and you moved up the ladder?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Yes. I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 caretaker}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  assistant at - when I went back to them from buses. And finished as chief assistant at Cliff Castle, which is deputy to the Director.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So how long would you be at Cliff Castle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 From it opening until 1965 which is - roughly five years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And you'd been at Victoria Park?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 From 1932 'til '60.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Twenty eight years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So altogether you were about thirty-three years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 As assistant curator?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 That\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 To one museum?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Then the other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Would you have preferred any other type of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You enjoyed being curator?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You preferred it to engineering?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh certainly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And that's why you went back to it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You served an apprenticeship at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 Wilkinson\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you serve a sort of training period to being a curator?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Yes. And the other one of course is what's built up during the years naturally, it's nearly a lifetime in it isn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So you've been learning all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 All the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 As new things have been added?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You've been taxidermist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. You don't do that now, no. It was the setting up of cases, exhibits and the preservation of exhibits and stuff like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 It's a sort of industrial museum to a certain extent now isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Well it's natural history and - local }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 industries.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So you would have to learn all about local industries as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 They also have exhibitions of art so would you have to learn something about art?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, I hadn't anything to do with the art section. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you belong to any trade union or professional organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Which one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 The A.S.E.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 That's the engineering union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Were you in the engineering union when you worked for the corporation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I remained in the engineering union and still in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Even while you were a curator?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. I' - and a member of N.A.L.G.O. then as well. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 So }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347 you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
 were a member of the engineering union and N.A.L.G.O.?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 When you worked the corporation as a curator?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. Yes
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And just the engineering union when you were}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10042093\charrsid2571347  working}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  on the buses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes. I'm still in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you take part in any of its activities, either N.A.L.G.O. or the engineering union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you feel that the employers and workers had the same interests or different? When you were at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 Wilkinson\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
Well this was a very peculiar time of course because as I say we - they were in a desperate war at that time and - when you're in a war like that the employers and the employees have forgot all about fighting one another haven't they. As 
a general rule. Yes. I mean the more interested in fighting the common enemy.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 When you worked for the corporation did you feel to have the same interest as the corporation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Oh yes, yes. I didn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 The well being of the museum?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 
Did you feel that there were divisions of interest among the workers, some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers, did you feel that or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Well there is, or was, yes, definitely there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Could you enlarge on that at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 The point was that when apprentices served their time as they called it or their apprenticeship and become a skilled }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15925974\charrsid2571347 craftsman}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347  they definitely thought they were superior to anyone who hadn't served an apprenticeship.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 I don't think it did because - I'd gone back to something that I wanted to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You were enjoying doing it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you continue to live at home after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 And with your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you spend your Sundays any differently, did you start going to church perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 You never went to church or chapel?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Did you start to take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3165056 FS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10433480 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6961456\charrsid2571347 This is the period immediately before 1919, what were your views then of politics?
